            h3 Danny
            p Co-Founder
            p.member-bio "I wanted to create a place where students and locals could find affordable, reliable bikes without the hassle."
          
          .team-member
            h3 Perri
            p Co-Founder
            p.member-bio "Building a community for bike enthusiasts is my goal. Let's keep SF riding green!"

